1.2
log
@- long overdue update of gv to 3.7.1.
among the many fixes are security fixes for CVE-2002-0838, CVE-2006-5864,
CVE-2010-2055 and CVE-2010-2056
- tweak DESCR
- fix MASTER_SITES/HOMEPAGE
- update license version
@
